{"tid":903872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家最癲試過喺公眾場合做啲乜？","createTime":"2018-11-16T02:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T02:49:19.000Z","uid":106001,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27ced586958419c7894df902101b38a9c7c49b19","tid":903872,"uid":106001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"記得兩年前上一堂tutor要用電腦嘅<br />\n我同個groupmate用中間最前2部電腦<br />\n咁上上吓堂個groupmate諗住玩鳩我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =groupmate<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂靖靖我搵到呢題點做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSend咗條link俾我<br />\n我用學校電腦開咗條link<br />\n點知係三個黑鬼互含片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢笑到仆街<br />\n但我冇熄條link仲繼續由佢播<br />\n咁個professor好鍾意周圍行睇吓啲同學有冇唔識<br />\n佢就慢慢行緊過黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲笑緊：喂啊sir黎緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我(望住個moon冇反應)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始緊張：喂屌啊sir黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我(望住個moon冇反應)<br />\nProfessor仲有3/4步就到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好緊張想控我滑鼠熄左佢但我hold實咗隻滑鼠<br />\n我groupmate即刻扮晒野望返自己個moon扮做緊野<br />\n跟住我喺個moon反射見到professor望咗我個moon一眼dup低頭唔出聲就走咗<br />\n跟住一路企喺原地發牛豆<br />\n過一陣有人舉手嗌佢好似嚇一嚇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加諗返轉頭都覺得自己好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知自己嗰時諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e3cf0badafc3ff3c976a70467e30d9f91c2e23","tid":903872,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f41f9c43c3763ae5fa2eafb3412db3bf7e